      <title>德國漢高因第一季業績強勁而上調 2024 年前景</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/germanys-henkel-raises-sales-earnings-outlook-2024-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德國消費品公司漢高週五小幅上調了2024年的預期，稱第一季的強勁表現提振了其銷售和獲利前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/germanys-henkel-raises-sales-earnings-outlook-2024-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 08:06:02 GMT</pubDate>
