      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-reports-26-rise-quarterly-room-revenue-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[假日酒店所有者洲際酒店集團 (IHG) 週五公佈第一季客房收入增長 2.6%，並表示繼續預計休閒旅遊需求將保持強勁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihg-reports-26-rise-quarterly-room-revenue-2024-05-03/</guid>
